verses.verse: The YY <S%H3068><s%> reigneth <S%H4427><s%> <S%H8804><s%>; let the people <S%H5971><s%> tremble <S%H7264><s%> <S%H8799><s%>: he sitteth <S%H3427><s%> <S%H8802><s%> between the cherubims <S%H3742><s%>; let the earth <S%H776><s%> be moved <S%H5120><s%> <S%H8799><s%>.
